<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>My Web Page</title>
    <style>
      .content {
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .content__card {
        flex: 0 0 300px;
        margin: 1rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .content__card img {
        width: 100%;
        transform: scale(1.1);
        transition: transform 0.7s ease;
      }

      .content__card:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.125);
      }

      .content__text {
        color: white;
        flex: 0 0 400px;
        margin: 1rem;
      }

      .content__text h2 {
        font-family: azo-sans-uber, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: normal;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .content__text p {
        font-family: azo-sans-web, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        font-style: normal;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: 200;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .content__buttons {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: left;
      }

      .content__buttons button {
        color: white;
        font-family: azo-sans-web, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        font-style: normal;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
        background-color: #2c4dde;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 14px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 9999px;
      }

      .content__buttons button a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
      }

      #normal {
        background-color: #090d2b;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #2c4dde;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="content">
      <div class="content__card">
        <img src="src/pages/images/start.jpg" alt="Card Image" />
      </div>
      <div class="content__text">
        <h2>
          Share your thoughts about books at <span class="highlight"
            >Bookreviewz!</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p>
          sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes nascetur
          ridiculus mus mauris vitae ultricies leo integer malesuada nunc vel
          risus
        </p>
        <div class="content__buttons">
          <button><a href="http://localhost:3000/Signin">Sign in</a></button>
          <button id="normal"
            ><a href="http://localhost:3000/Signup">Sign up</a></button
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
